## Testing Checklist

Before submitting a new widget:

**Functionality:**
- [ ] Widget renders without errors
- [ ] Loading state displays correctly
- [ ] Error handling works (test with network offline)
- [ ] Refresh button updates data
- [ ] Data persists across page refreshes (if using widget settings)

**UI/UX:**
- [ ] Widget works in light + dark mode
- [ ] Text is readable (WCAG AA contrast)
- [ ] Responsive design (test at different widget sizes)
- [ ] Animations smooth (no jank)
- [ ] Keyboard navigation works (Tab, Enter, ESC)

**Performance:**
- [ ] No excessive re-renders (check with React DevTools Profiler)
- [ ] API calls debounced/throttled (if user input)
- [ ] Bundle size impact < 50KB (check with `npm run build`)
- [ ] Lazy loading used for heavy dependencies

**Accessibility:**
- [ ] Semantic HTML used (`<button>`, `<nav>`, `<article>`)
- [ ] ARIA labels present
- [ ] Focus states visible
- [ ] Screen reader friendly (test with NVDA/JAWS)

