## Widget Categories

Choose the most appropriate category for your widget:

**`core`** - Core app integrations (Notes, Calendar, Tasks)
- Examples: Recent Notes, Upcoming Events
- Always useful, enabled by default

**`productivity`** - Productivity tools and utilities
- Examples: Pomodoro Timer, World Clock, Currency Converter, Quote of the Day
- Helps users work more efficiently

**`news`** - News and information feeds
- Examples: Hacker News, Reddit, Dev.to, Wikipedia
- Keeps users informed

**`finance`** - Financial data and tracking
- Examples: Crypto Tracker, Stock Market
- Displays market data

**`fun`** - Games and entertainment
- Examples: Memory Game, Typing Test, Developer Jokes
- Provides breaks and entertainment

**`visual`** - Visual and creative tools
- Examples: Weather Map, Unsplash Photos
- Emphasizes visual design

**`dev`** - Developer tools and information
- Examples: GitHub Trending, NPM Stats, Repo Stats
- Developer-focused content

**`utility`** - Utilities and tools
- Examples: Calculator, QR Code Generator, Unit Converter, IP Info
- General-purpose utilities

